<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>mount on navyd的个人博客</title><link>https://blog.navyd.xyz/tags/mount/</link><description>Recent content in mount on navyd的个人博客</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 09 May 2022 22:49:19 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://blog.navyd.xyz/tags/mount/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Mounting Practice on Linux</title><link>https://blog.navyd.xyz/post/2022/05/09/mounting-practice-on-linux/</link><pubDate>Mon, 09 May 2022 22:49:19 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://blog.navyd.xyz/post/2022/05/09/mounting-practice-on-linux/</guid><description>&lt;p>有一个需求，由于raspi4 home目录所在的dev空间容量不足达到90%，需要更换更大容量的dev。当前在系统中已挂载了一个4T的USB dev在/mnt/share/中，想在USB dev中直接划分一个目录挂载到/home中即可，mount的bind最合适&lt;/p>
&lt;p>但是，在挂载后出现问题无法执行bin：&lt;code>mount zsh: permission denied: bin&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">$ mount --bind /mnt/share/home/navyd /home/navyd
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">$ bin
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">mount zsh: permission denied: bin
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
